MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2003-2036. State v. Barton.

Warren C.P. No. 03CR20526. On motion to dissolve stay on ruling upon motion for leave to file supplemental proposition of law. Motion to dissolve stay granted. On motion for leave to file supplemental proposition of law. Motion denied.

Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents and would deny the motion to dissolve stay.
